data.description: You'll feel right at home with this beautiful single story floor-plan in the heart of The Colony. Offering 3 spacious bedrooms, 2 bedrooms, and a backyard with a covered patio, this home is made to entertain. Situated just [5 minutes] from Grandscape, you'll have access to an array of shopping, dining, and entertainment options at your fingertips. Additionally, within [15 minutes], you'll find yourself at PGA, Toyota Stadium, and the upcoming Universal Studios, providing endless opportunities for leisure and recreation.
